                </svg>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <section class="py-16 bg-base-200">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="join join-vertical w-full">
          <div class="collapse collapse-arrow join-item">
            <input type="radio" name="my-accordion-4" checked="checked" /> 
            <div class="collapse-title text-xl font-medium text-left">
              How long does it take to build an MVP?
            </div>
            <div class="collapse-content text-left"> 
              <p>Our MVP development typically takes 2-8 weeks depending on the complexity of your project. Our starter package MVPs can be delivered in as little as 2 weeks, while more complex projects may take longer.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="collapse collapse-arrow join-item">
            <input type="radio" name="my-accordion-4" /> 
            <div class="collapse-title text-xl font-medium text-left">
              What happens after the MVP is built?
            </div>
            <div class="collapse-content text-left"> 
              <p>After your MVP is launched, we help you collect user feedback and can continue working with you to iterate on your product. We offer ongoing development packages to help you scale your MVP based on real user data.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="collapse collapse-arrow join-item">
            <input type="radio" name="my-accordion-4" /> 
            <div class="collapse-title text-xl font-medium text-left">
              Do you provide design services?
            </div>
            <div class="collapse-content text-left"> 
              <p>Yes, our packages include design services to ensure your MVP is not only functional but also provides a great user experience. Our team includes experienced designers who specialize in creating intuitive interfaces.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
